snippet.textDisplay: Can you make White Castle frozen sliders? I grew up in Minnesota with them as my favourite food but when I was adopted and moved to Oregon there were no white castles in sight. Because of the absence of my favourite restaurant I have found the frozen version which is honestly sub-par but it still takes me back to the good times. There are ways to make them a bit better but I need to be able to actually make them to satiate the hole inside my heart. It would make me really excited if you did this💕
